* Email notification

Should probably have some backoff so we don't send email continuously.

* Command pipe

With a different command mode for the main program (or possibly a different
program) that can be used to send commands to the main process in order to
control the child.

* Fix the debian package source check

At the end of "make deb", lintian complains about not being able to check the
created source package.  Find out if this is a problem with the use of
git-buildpackage, or a problem in debian/ubuntu.
